{
  "stem": "7600.4",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I find-- I found a little-- a young man, and his name was Mr.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Feder, F-E-D-E-R.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I never forgot him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he said, oh, you have everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I'll help you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I'll try and get it for you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He said, but it will take a couple of weeks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But don't give up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We'll get it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "If you have everything, there's no reason-- and you're-- you're 17.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I mean, there's no reason why they should-- they're going to keep you here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You want to go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I mean, you're not man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You're not anything that they want.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So he says, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I'll get it for you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then he-- he wrote-- then he-- he wrote me a letter saying, be in such and such a building-- that was the [?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Rothschild ?] building that the Nazis had taken over-- at 9:00 on this and this date.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was there at 8:30.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as soon as I got there, there were two Nazis standing there-- soldiers-- with open bayonets.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was closed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I went very furtively up to the steps and I said, I have an appointment with Mr.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Feder in here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "No, everything's closed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I just went down the stairs again and I stood there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then a few other people came.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They all-- he probably had other people that he had promised to get.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we had a little crowd, like maybe 10 people, maybe 12, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I didn't count.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were all talking to each other, saying, Mr.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Feder had promised to get you the exit visa.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They're all exit visas that he had promised to get.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were standing there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was a misty November day, I am quite sure.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
